{"tid":1753983,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人到左今日 就後悔尋日投左泛民","createTime":"2019-11-25T05:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T10:52:37.000Z","uid":184722,"like":1,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0d71f9504d44f8b4211ac5f461e515154268de35","tid":1753983,"uid":184722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"老實講 <br />\n如果無尼場運動<br />\n我一定投對家<br />\n我對泛民既憎恨已經超過左對建制派<br />\n唔單止係泛民本身<br />\n更甚既係一班支持者<br />\n實在係太撚柒啦！<br />\n<br />\n但係今次運動之後<br />\n我對部分泛民議員已經改觀<br />\n但係部分泛民議員我仍然覺得係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n尋日算係半含投票 <br />\n見到好多建制大佬拉左落台<br />\n係開心左一陣<br />\n<br />\n但今日又見到d泛民打手出黎清算獻世<br />\n我真係屌你老母<br />\n尋日有人都係含住投架啦<br />\n加上係場運動下無辦法焗住撐你<br />\n唔通真係貪你做得野咩？<br />\n<br />\n到左今日贏左dd就走出黎吠<br />\n究竟你班泛狗仲要趕走幾多人？"},{"pid":"bb721c794ad1bea6941401772226ad5be706625c","tid":1753983,"uid":323658,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:28:47.000Z","msg":"冇呀 屌你老母"},{"pid":"1bd84e5095a27a7a95f9173a7b515b4d39b66421","tid":1753983,"uid":108462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"冇 sor"},{"pid":"bc656c3d7e2fc727601286dad4c6ad54dccd057b","tid":1753983,"uid":310765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a913feb4a313a2f0392acc90c5d47137cb620fc","tid":1753983,"uid":69916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"d5c1b7dff44ccf90d52321cec7c1ae58794547ea","tid":1753983,"uid":2697,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"我就後悔入嚟浪費我30秒睇你篇垃圾文"},{"pid":"eeb7d21310d81036ded6a0f3ff1abd2555ad1d0b","tid":1753983,"uid":118665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:33:40.000Z","msg":"拉，打敗建制第一，清算泛民第二。目前都唔清算住。"},{"pid":"f8814e82ef1b3a298aba8530845c80a030a58383","tid":1753983,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:37:34.000Z","